{"id":518562,"date":[{"year":1972,"month":6,"day":1}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"风雷激(纪念毛主席的光辉著作《在延安文艺座谈会上的讲话》发表三十周年征文选刊)","column":"","genre":"","count":"732","ytitle":"","mtitle":"工人新村的歌(儿歌四首)","ftitle":"","authors":["张秋生"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"张秋生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新村后面有间房"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新村后面有间房，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烂草屋顶泥巴墙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大风吹，摇三摇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"外面下雨里面淌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这间屋，没人住，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留在这里啥用场?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啥用场?听我讲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里可是好课堂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"退休工人老爷爷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常给我们把课上:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我们今天住新村，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一排一排高楼房。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻身不能忘过去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过去这里啥模样?——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"臭水沟，破草房，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蚊蝇成群多荒凉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动人民做牛马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饥寒交迫恨满腔……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多亏党和毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领导咱们打豺狼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻了身，当了家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还给咱们造楼房。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留下这间破屋子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是一本血泪账，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看着它，眼明亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级斗争永不忘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟着党和毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命到底不迷航。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爷爷没退休"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爷爷今年六十九，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从早到晚四处走。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"里弄组织学习班，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"认真读书他带头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学校召开忆苦会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请他诉诉血泪仇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们办起小小班，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他又是个好参谋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宣传革命样板戏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爷爷可真有一手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"演个海港马洪亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大伙夸个不停口。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爷爷越老心越红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命路上雄赳赳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说爷爷退休了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我家爷爷没退休!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"外宾叔叔来参观"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘟嘟嘟，喇叭响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红小兵，齐鼓掌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"外宾叔叔来参观，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"友谊歌声传四方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叔叔搂住我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和我把话讲——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问我从小关心啥?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长大要干那一行?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“世界地图墙上挂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五洲风雷胸中装，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们红小兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心明眼又亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身在教室眼望全球，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"努力学习斗志昂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长大要当工农兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为世界革命献力量。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叔叔听了乐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连声来夸奖:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“从小懂得干革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这样的接班人可"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真棒!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好孩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笃、笃、笃……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“谁敲门?”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“王大爷，是我们。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“大强和小华，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们来迟啦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东东刚刚擦完窗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小军就来洗衣裳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平平、小琴抢着干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帮我拎水拖地板。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活儿全都干完啦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们好好休息吧。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“军属王大爷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们都知道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最近你生病，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"应该来照料。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是小小理发员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拥军优属记心间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上门来服务，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工具带得全，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是技术不大高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要请大爷提意见。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你们完全彻底为人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真是毛主席的红小兵!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入6号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1972\\06\\7261030201.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入6号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1972\\06\\7261030202.JPG\">"}]}